                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2591" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0562</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共建美好的全联接世界——华为的开放式创新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Build a beautiful and fully connected world——The way of open innovation of HUAWEI</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘顿，王冰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国科学技术大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华为</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华为；开放式创新；商业模式；机遇与挑战</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HUAWEI; open innovation; business models; opportunities andchallenges</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着经济全球化的加深和技术创新的快速发展，传统的仅依赖企业内部资源的“封闭式创新”模式，已经无法适应复杂多变的市场需求与消费者偏好。企业开始与供应商、消费者、甚至竞争对手建立合作关系，由“封闭”走向“开放”，采用“开放式创新”模式。本案例真实地再现了华为的开放式创新实践之路，从华为面临的困境、开放式创新战略的确定到华为现今的累累硕果，按照华为“以奋斗者为本，以客户为中心，以共建全联接世界为愿景”的指导思想，从微观、中观以及宏观三个层面对华为的开放式创新模式和发展过程进行了系统的描述。旨在从华为企业的商业实践中，引导MBA学员利用开放式创新、商业模式等理论对开放式创新的模式选择、合作方式、战略目标等展开分析，对开放式创新对企业创新的应用进行探讨，同时对开放式创新中的机遇与挑战进行展望。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the deepening of economic globalization and the rapid development of technological innovation, the traditional &quot;closed innovation&quot; mode, which only rely on the internal resources of enterprises, has been unable to adapt to the complex and ever-changing market demand and consumer preferences. Enterprises began to establish cooperative relations with suppliers, consumers, and even competitors, from &quot;closed&quot; to &quot;open&quot;, using &quot;open innovation&quot; model. In this case, a true representation of the HUAWEI open innovation practice, open from the predicament of HUAWEI, innovation strategy to determine the HUAWEI current fruitful, according to HUAWEI &quot;to strive for this, take the customer as the center, to build a fully connected world vision&quot; guiding ideology, the system the description from the micro, meso and macro three aspects of HUAWEI&#39;s open innovation and development process. Aimed at HUAWEI&#39;s enterprise business practice, guide MBA students use open innovation and business model theory, the open innovation mode of cooperation, the strategic target of analysis, discusses the application of open innovation of enterprise innovation, and the opportunities and challenges of open innovation in the future.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》、《管理学》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司层战略制定 技术创新管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-12</td>
                            </tr>
